enable

public GnLog enable(GnLogPackageType arg0)
             throws GnException
Enable logging for the given package with the current logging options and filters. Enable can be called multiple times to enable logging of multiple packages to the same log.

Remarks:

Changes to logging options and filters do not take affect until the logger is next enabled.

Parameters:
package - [in] GnLogPackage to enable for this log.
Returns:
This GnLog object to allow method chaining.
Throws:
GnException
